Package TLC.CompilerWhile

Class Visitor

java.lang.Object
TLC.CompilerWhile.Visitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
PrinterVisitor, SymbolTableVisitor, ThreeAdressesVisitor
public class Visitor extends Object
This class is an abstract class that is used to visit a CommonTree Based on the tokens of the tree, it will redirect the call of the visit method to the right method the visitor works with other classes representing the tokens
